 AVRGame project contains the following modules and games:
==========================================================
  Schematics
  Configuration
  Cross platform utilityes
  Global variables
  Graphics display driver and fonts
  Joystick
  Pong game
  Quarth game
  Snake game
  Tetris game

 Known issues:
===============
  * No collision detection in down moving ball in Pong game.
  * Only buttom of tetromino collision detection in tetris game.

 Features:
===========
  * AVRGame is compatible with Codvision and gcc-avr compilers.
